* {{man|3|strlcpy|OpenBSD|size-bounded string copying and concatenation}}
* [http://undeadly.org/cgi?action=article&sid=20060405212010&mode=flat Developer Blog discussion of <tt>strlcpy</tt> and <tt>mempcpy</tt>]

