==NPN Transistor== NPN Transistor is a Semi Conductor Device made from Semi Conductor materials which has 3 pins Base, Collector, Emmiter forming 2 junctions namely BE and CE
==NPN Transistor == NPN Transistor is made by joining one Positive-Typed Semi Conductor in between two Negative-Typed Semi Conductors :[[File:NPN_BJT.svg|300px]]
==Symbol== :[[File:BJT_symbol_NPN.svg|50px]] {{BookCat}}

==PNP Transistor== PNP Transistor is a Semi Conductor Device made from Semi Conductor materials which has 3 pins Base, Collector, Emmiter forming 2 junctions namely BE and CE
==Construction== PNP Transistor is made by joining one Nagative-Typed Semi Conductor in between two Positive-Typed Semi Conductors : [[File:PNP_BJT.svg|300px]]
==Symbol== :[[File:BJT_symbol_PNP.svg|50px]] {{BookCat}}

==P-channel JFET==
P-Channel JFET has a similar construction where N and P regions of N-Channel JFET are swapped.
{{BookCat}}

